definition: not having undergone/without (having gone though a certain process)
not yet/did not/have not/not/8th earthly branch: 1-3 p.m., 6th solar month (7th July-6th August), year of the Sheep/ancient Chinese compass point: 210°
classics/sacred book/scripture/to pass through/to undergo/to bear/to endure/warp (textile)/longitude/menstruation/channel (TCM)/abbr. for economics 經濟|经济[jing1 ji4]

sentences.english: Unsolicited advice is perceived as annoying. Don’t do it.
sentences.chinese: 未經請求的建議也會令人討厭，所以不要那麼做。

sentences.english: Article 66 The trustee of a public trust must not resign without the approval of the regulatory agency of public undertakings.
sentences.chinese: 信託的受託人未經公益事業管理機構批准，不得辭任。

sentences.english: No unit or individual may have cultural relics transferred without approval.
sentences.chinese: 未經批准，任何單位或者個人不得調取文物。

sentences.english: Google this year began to automatically transfer Chinese users to an uncensored website in Hong Kong.
sentences.chinese: 今年開始將中國用戶自動跳轉到未經審查的香港網站。

sentences.english: You cannot be transferred to another employer or employment without the approval of the CLA.
sentences.chinese: 您未經勞委會許可不得轉換僱主及工作。

sentences.english: How dare you borrow it without my permission?
sentences.chinese: 你怎麼敢未經我允許把它借走呢？

sentences.english: There are unconfirmed reports that the two people have been shot in the neighboring town.
sentences.chinese: 未經證實的報道說在附近城鎮有兩個人遭到槍殺。

sentences.english: How dare you enter this building without permition .
sentences.chinese: 未經允許你怎麼敢進入這幢大樓呢？

sentences.english: It's not moral to read the personal letter without permission.
sentences.chinese: 未經允許拆閱個人信件不道德。

sentences.english: This unsolicited commercial e-mail message is sent to your domain.
sentences.chinese: 此未經請求的商業電子郵件消息被髮送到您的域。

sentences.english: Replace the mechanical devices and settings without the written approval of LCF.
sentences.chinese: 未經本公司書面批准，更改機械上裝置與設定。

sentences.english: No person shall override safety interlocks without proper authorization.
sentences.chinese: 任何人不得未經授權旁路安全聯鎖。

sentences.english: Many untreated wounds are becoming infected, leading to amputations.
sentences.chinese: 許多未經治療的傷員正遭受感染，會導致截肢。

sentences.english: Alterations to the terms of an insurance shall not be made without the approval of the Project Manager.
sentences.chinese: 未經建築師許可，不能擅自變更保險條款。

sentences.english: Characterized by an authoritative, arrogant assertion of unproved or unprovable principles.
sentences.chinese: 在爭論中作爲前提提出的未經證明的陳述。

sentences.english: Uncertified alterations or erasures shall invalidate the certificates.
sentences.chinese: 證書未經證明而塗改應屬無效。
